{"id":441787,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":30}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"178","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我领到一支步枪","ftitle":"","authors":["巫惟格"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"巫惟格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以民兵的名义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领到了一支步枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一支老式的步枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我握着它，象握着宝贝一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪身满是刀伤弹痕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是记录了血与火的革命斗争；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪口经子弹磨擦而发青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先辈用它消灭过多少敌人?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滑溜溜的木柄上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下深深的指印，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是刻着战士对敌人的仇恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是刻着战士对革命的忠诚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，它的先前主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许战斗在新的岗位上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许早已牺牲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下枪，教育我们……"}]}